com.psddev.dari.util

Class AmazonStorageItem

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.psddev.dari.util.AbstractStorageItem
      • com.psddev.dari.util.AmazonStorageItem
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    SettingsBackedObject, StorageItem

    public class AmazonStorageItem
extends AbstractStorageItem
    StorageItem stored in Amazon S3.

    To use this class, it must be able to access the JetS3t library. If you use Maven, you should add the following dependency:

    <dependency>
    <groupId>net.java.dev.jets3t</groupId>
    <artifactId>jets3t</artifactId>
    <version>0.8.0</version>
</dependency>
